text: Hans Haasmann (6 January 1916 - 26 May 2008) was a Dutch diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Dutch male divers Category:Olympic divers of the Netherlands Category:Divers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Jakarta
